{"tid":810881,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓爆2018】「美聯樓價指數」最新報176.38點,按周只升約0.21%","createTime":"2018-09-08T10:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T11:08:04.000Z","uid":43146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff2de19f3cee8916c8069dc122cf33da1d4f962c","tid":810881,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 「美聯樓價指數」最新報176.38點,按周升約0.21%;較4星期前則微減約0.05%。目前「美聯樓價指數」高位整固,自7月上旬衝破175點後,至今已連續9星期徘徊於逾175點至逾176點水平,而年內迄今樓價仍累積上升約12.32%。<br />\n<br />\n「美聯樓價指數」按周上升,受九龍及新界帶動。「美聯新界樓價指數」最新報167.99點,按周升約0.33%;相較4星期前亦升約0.31%;而年內迄今累升約14.27%。九龍區方面,「美聯九龍樓價指數」最新報166.66點,按周升約0.2%;縱使與4星期前相比跌約0.97%,惟年內迄今仍升約10.51%。<br />\n<br />\n反觀,港島為唯一樓價按周回落的區份。「美聯港島樓價指數」最新報191.01點,按周跌約1.49%;比起4星期前更跌約1.56%;年內迄今仍累升約10.07%。 (BC)"},{"pid":"a327787aa2633d1ae78ab23d6c4ae5366edbb496","tid":810881,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲升緊 樓市gogogo"},{"pid":"201edf5115b501f9636a75dd683a83549645adf2","tid":810881,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a327787aa2633d1ae78ab23d6c4ae5366edbb496","tid":810881,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲升緊 樓市gogogo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"0.21%, 唔計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58488bd6dc09d1e3e063b16172ccc4f2b6c30f89","tid":810881,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:08:04.000Z","msg":"劈價樓盤唔計"}]}